{
  "chapter": 55,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十五回\"剑痴情绝\"。独孤痴发现每日服侍他的\"孩子\"小燕竟是个美丽女子，但他并未表现出惊讶。小方出现，与独孤痴展开了一场剑客间的对话。小方指出他们因命运锁链而被绑在一起——他、独孤痴、小燕和卜鹰。小方坦言将追随独孤痴，而独孤痴则警告会伺机杀他，这反而被小方视为认可。两人一同前往大漠寻找卜鹰埋藏的黄金。途中在风化山岩下等待日出，以石头影子定位宝藏。夜间突然出现自称\"鬼魂\"的神秘势力，声称守护卜鹰的黄金。小方和独孤痴联手迎战，识破敌人并非卜鹰属下（因直呼其名而非称\"鹰哥\"），双方展开激烈交锋。独孤痴一剑刺杀南面敌人，小方则斩杀西方持枪者。两人在险境中默契配合，以言语诱敌暴露位置，展现出剑客的细心与果断。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你来迟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "是的。今天我是来迟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "命运就像条锁链，有时往往会将一些本来完全没有关系的人锁在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "现在我们已经全都被锁住了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们？我们是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "你、我、她、卜鹰。从现在起，不管你要到哪里去，我都会在你附近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "因为我知道你也跟我一样，要去找卜鹰。所以我相信，不管我走到哪里，你一定也会在我附近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "只要我们两个人不死，她一定会来找我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你不怕我杀了你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我不怕。我知道你也不会出手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "因为你也没把握杀我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你变了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "是的，我变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "从前我从未将你看成我的对手，可是现在……现在或许有人会认为你已变成个懦夫，但是我却认为你变成个剑客。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你说的不错，从现在开始我们也许真的已经被锁在一起，所以你一定要特别注意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我要特别注意？注意什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "注意我。从现在开始，我一有机会就会杀了你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这地方我已待不下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我就要走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我跟着你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你错了。不管你要到哪里去，我都跟着你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你还记不记得我们第一次相见的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你还找不找得到那地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "你还记不记得这块石头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "黄金就在下面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "不在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你为什么在这里停下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "黄金是卜鹰和班察巴那埋藏的，知道这秘密的本来就只有他们两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是现在你也知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "因为卜鹰也把我带到了埋藏黄金的地方。他带我去的时候，已经是深夜。我们走的时候，天却已亮了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "那时太阳刚升起，刚好将这块石头的影子，照在埋藏黄金的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方伟，独孤痴，你们走吧！最好快走，越快越好。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是什么人？为什么要我们走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自从蚩尤战死，宝藏被掘后，世上每一宗巨大的宝藏，都有幽灵鬼魂在看守。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们就是替卜鹰看守这一批黄金宝藏的鬼魂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都是为卜鹰战死的人。我们活着时是战士，死了也是厉鬼。我们绝不容任何人侵犯他的黄金。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果我们不想走呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你们就要死在这里了。而且死得很惨。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白你的意思。只可惜你们说的话我连一句都不信。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们说的话你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信？我连一句都不信！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你不妨先看看这些人。因为你很快就会变得跟他们一样了，他们也是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "好快的剑；好狠的出手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "彼此彼此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是我不懂你为什么要下毒手？你知道他不是卜鹰的属下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "text": "卜鹰的属下从来没有人敢直呼他的名字。大家都叫他鹰哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "想不到你居然还很细心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_chi",
      "speaker_name": "独孤痴",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "像我们这种人，一定要细心，才能活得长些。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 374
    }
  ],
